Title: Edge of Evil
Description: After being accused of murder, suspect Adam North asks the victim's best friend, Petrocelli to defend him.
Short Description: Suspected murderer asks Petrocelli, the victim's friend, to defend him.

Title: Once Upon a Victim
Description: Dr. Leo is arrested for murdering Rita Philips, the main financial supporter of Dr. Leo's hospital. The motive should be the end of support, but Petrocelli thinks the real killer must have a better motive.
Short Description: Petrocelli takes the case of a suspect accused of murdering his leading supporter.

Title: Counterploy
Description: Pete's friend John Deiman is a cop who is said to have murdered his wife's lover but insists he's innocent so Pete asks Tony to help him out.
Short Description: Petrocelli takes the case of a cop suspected of murder.

Title: By Reason of Madness
Description: Petrocelli defends a wife accused of killing her husband. She knows she killed him but says she didn't know she was doing it. Petrocelli soon realizes she was mentally ill and has to prove her not guilty by reason of insanity.
Short Description: Petrocelli defends a wife accused of killing her husband.

Title: A Fallen Idol
Description: Tony's childhood friend Frankie Copa (now a professional boxer) needs a defense attorney after his manager is beaten to death and Frankie is found on the scene.
Short Description: Petrocelli's boxer friend is suspected of killing his manager

Title: Showdown
Description: The Cartwrights unknowingly hire a bank robber to work at the Ponderosa. Only Joe is suspicious.
Short Description: Little Joe is suspicious of a new hire at the Ponderosa

Title: The Last Viking
Description: Hoss’ Uncle Gunnar arrives at the Ponderosa on a visit, bringing more than just memories with him.

Title: Desert Justice
Description: A Ponderosa ranch hand is arrested and taken away for trial. Adam and Hoss go along.
Short Description: Hoss and Little Joe accompany a ranch hand accused of murder.

Title: Badge Without Honor
Description: A hired killer poses as Deputy Marshal to take a friend of Ben’s to Sacramento for a trial, really meaning to kill him.
Short Description: A fake U.S. marshal takes Ben's friend to Sacramento for a fake trial and real murder.

Title: Escape to Ponderosa
Description: Three men who escaped from an army prison take refuge at the Ponderosa from an unlikable commanding officer.
Short Description: Three soldiers escape Army prison and an abusive commanding officer.

Title: Hercules: the animated movie
Description: Hercules performs his Labors, sails with the Argonauts, and romances the fair Iole.
Short Description: Hercules performs his Labors, sails with the Argonauts, and romances the fair Iole.

Title: Prisoners of the Lost Planet: the animated movie
Description: Three people are transported into a parallel reality, where they find they must use modern technology, but medieval weapons, in order to save the citizenry from a murderous warlord.
Short Description: Three people are transported into a parallel reality.

Title: TNT! the animated movie
Description: A young karate expert searches for her brother's killer in Hong Kong.
Short Description: A young karate expert searches for her brother's killer in Hong Kong.
